{"type":"message","id":"1443855b","parentId":"02c4d1c4","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:40:34.663Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"搜索功能不可用。不过我可以提供已知的飞书下载地址信息。\n\n飞书/Lark 的官方下载地址是：\n- 中国版（飞书）：https://www.feishu.cn/download\n- 国际版（Lark）：https://www.larksuite.com/download\n\n让我直接帮用户打开浏览器到下载页面，或者提供下载链接。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"没有搜索 API，不过我可以直接帮你打开飞书官方下载页面："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf55ffadf5c31d1ef2fe22c8d9f73","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"open","url":"https://www.feishu.cn/download","profile":"user"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":355,"output":190,"cacheRead":15104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15649,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773643224362}}
