{"type":"message","id":"3cf051e1","parentId":"71de80c3","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:40:54.492Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"浏览器无法连接，Chrome 可能没有运行。那我就直接告诉用户飞书的下载地址吧。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"浏览器暂时连不上。这是飞书官方下载地址：\n\n**🇨🇳 飞书（中国版）**\n- 官网：https://www.feishu.cn/download\n- Windows/Mac/手机端都有\n\n**🌍 Lark（国际版）**\n- 官网：https://www.larksuite.com/download\n\n直接去官网下载安装包就行。你是 Windows 电脑，点 Windows 客户端下载即可。\n\n需要我帮你用命令行下载安装包吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":229,"output":148,"cacheRead":15424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15801,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773643242222}}
