{"type":"message","id":"9b1324b6","parentId":"865c4134","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:44:05.552Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我帮他下载并安装飞书。我可以使用 PowerShell 命令来下载飞书的安装包，然后运行安装程序。\n\n飞书的下载链接通常是 https://www.feishu.cn/download，但具体的 Windows 安装包下载链接我需要找到。飞书 Windows 客户端通常是一个 .exe 安装程序。\n\n让我用 exec 来下载飞书安装包。我可以使用 curl 或 Invoke-WebRequest 来下载。飞书官方的 Windows 下载链接通常类似于：\nhttps://sf3-cn.feishucdn.com/obj/ee-tosa-admin/lark-electron-cn-stable-xxxx.exe\n\n但实际上，我可以先尝试用 PowerShell 下载飞书安装包。飞书的下载页面会重定向到实际的安装包链接。\n\n让我用 Invoke-WebRequest 来下载：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf5632f07a41ee8200ad277eff564","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Invoke-WebRequest -Uri \"https://www.feishu.cn/download\" -OutFile \"$env:TEMP\\feishu_download.html\" -UseBasicParsing; $content = Get-Content \"$env:TEMP\\feishu_download.html\" -Raw; Write-Output $content","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":451,"output":402,"cacheRead":15104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15957,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773643432725}}
