{"type":"message","id":"4551c4f4","parentId":"440911a6","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:45:04.351Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个HTML页面是一个JavaScript渲染的页面，下载链接不会直接出现在HTML源码中。我需要找到一个直接的下载链接。\n\n飞书的Windows客户端下载链接通常是通过API获取的重定向链接。让我尝试直接下载一个常见的飞书客户端安装包链接。飞书的Electron客户端通常有这样的模式：\n- Windows: https://sf3-cn.feishucdn.com/obj/goofy/lark/releases/lark_win32_ia32-xxx.exe 或类似的\n\n让我尝试直接用PowerShell下载飞书客户端。飞书提供了官方的下载地址格式：\n- 对于Windows，通常是：https://www.feishucdn.com/lark/artifacts/FeishuSetup.exe 或类似的\n\n让我尝试下载：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，让我直接下载飞书 Windows 客户端安装包："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf56409ff91cbda580f8df5c66fab","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$downloadUrl = \"https://sf3-cn.feishucdn.com/obj/goofy/lark-artifacts/dist/lark-desktop-7.32.9-ia32.exe\"; $outputPath = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Downloads\\FeishuSetup.exe\"; Write-Host \"正在下载飞书安装包...\"; try { Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $downloadUrl -OutFile $outputPath -UseBasicParsing; Write-Host \"下载完成: $outputPath\" } catch { Write-Host \"下载失败，尝试备用链接...\"; $downloadUrl2 = \"https://www.feishu.cn/suite/download/feishu/win32\"; Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $downloadUrl2 -OutFile $outputPath -UseBasicParsing -MaximumRedirection 5; Write-Host \"下载完成: $outputPath\" }","timeout":120}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":71738,"output":501,"cacheRead":15552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87791,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773643452034}}
